milestones.description: Dean Minors has broken the record for most sixes (2) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Tucker's 1
Dean Minors and Tucker's 36-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Tucker and Romaine
Lionel Cann and Hasan Durham's 38-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Dean Minors and Hasan Durham
Lionel Cann has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (2) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors's 1
Hasan Durham has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for BMUDA, going past Dean Minors
Dean Minors has broken the record for most dismissals (3) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Kwame Tucker's 2
This is the lowest match aggregate (435) involving teams Zimbabwe & Bermuda in ODIs

stories.title: Sibanda hundred secures victory for Zimbabwe
stories.subTitle: Bermuda v Zimbabwe, Tri-Nation ODI final , Trinidad
stories.summary: As expected, Zimbabwe cruised to victory over Bermuda in the final of the Tri-Nation tournament at Queen's Park Oval, Vusi Sibanda's hundred giving them a total that was never likely to be overtaken
